commit.message: Test on Ruby 2.7

Add project metadata to the gemspec

As per https://guides.rubygems.org/specification-reference/#metadata,
add metadata to the gemspec file. This'll allow people to more easily
access the source code, raise issues and read the changelog. These
bug_tracker_uri, changelog_uri, documentation_uri, source_code_uri, and
wiki_uri links will appear on the rubygems page at
https://rubygems.org/gems/rbnacl and be available via the rubygems API
after the next release.
